WEBVTT

00:01:58.728 --> 00:02:02.279
to those who prioritized
novel and sculptural forms,

00:02:02.303 --> 00:02:04.775
like ribbons, or ...

00:02:05.514 --> 00:02:06.673
pickles?

00:02:06.697 --> 00:02:09.006
(Laughter)

00:02:10.866 --> 00:02:13.357
And I think this
is supposed to be a snail.

00:02:14.530 --> 00:02:16.264
Something about this bothered me.

00:02:16.971 --> 00:02:20.914
Why was it that the best architects,
the greatest architecture --

00:02:20.938 --> 00:02:23.540
all beautiful and visionary
and innovative --

00:02:24.078 --> 00:02:26.249
is also so rare,

00:02:26.273 --> 00:02:28.720
and seems to serve so very few?

00:02:29.715 --> 00:02:31.212
And more to the point: